My thoughts on the Tir Tir foundation⬇️

If you are thinking of getting this then stop thinking and just get it!! It creates a super thin layer on the skin and doesn’t feel heavy at all. It’s also blurring and long lasting. 
I was not sure about my shade so I chose it randomly. It was slightly lighter but after a while it did oxidise a bit. 
Its definitely worth the hype and I’ve been using it ever since I got it😍😍 I got the mini one but getting the full size one once this gets overrr
